cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the impact of Batch Normalization on the convergence and generalization of neural networks, which are topics commonly studied in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper specifically focuses on the regularization aspect of Batch Normalization, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG.
